Class Summary
Directory Defines the user directory used by EBX5 for user authentication and roles management.
DirectoryDefault The default internal directory implementation that is delivered with EBX5.
DirectoryDefaultFactory The factory for the default internal implementation of the user and roles directory that is delivered with EBX5.
DirectoryFactory Factory for the user and roles directory.
DirectoryHandler An instance of this class wraps the current custom directory implementation, so as to add pre-processing and post-verifications to the directory method implementations.
ProfileListContext This class is used by a user and roles directory to customize the profiles that a user can select.
